what size blanket for my horse hey i know its a bit early for blanket shoppin but i was just wondering about what size blanket would fit my broadish paint gelding thanx get a cloth tape measure and measure from the center of his chest around to the center of his tail be sure to fit the tape around the largest part of the shoulder and hip generally takes two people to measure accurately don't guess at the size believe it or not too small in the shoulders causes blanket lameness Equine conformation Horse Sniper Casualty lifting Brassiere Shotgun Who Shot Mr. Burns? Mattress Dobermann B-47 Stratojet Comanche Compact audio cassette Normal distribution Sampling (music) My Life as a Teenage Robot Hey Jude Tyrannosaurus rex Great White Shark Captain Thunderbolt Milton H. Erickson The Jeffersons (South Park) ZAFT Armed Keeper of Unity Aerial (dance move) Crazy Horse Domestication of the horse Mixed-breed dog Chair Weight training Spanking Tightlacing Richard Nixon M16 (rifle) Tank Horse tack Mars Exploration Rover Kurt Cobain Internal ballistics Appaloosa Mr. Olympia Seabiscuit Password Late Night with Conan O'Brien Hubble Space Telescope Hat Drawing Professional wrestling throws Electrophysiology Password cracking Simile Professional wrestling holds Swingout Magnetic tape Cartridge (firearms) New Deal Plaid Native Americans in the United States Kilt Rich Mullins First aid kit Dog agility Handloading Contredanse Traveller (horse) Microphone Corset Lead and follow (dance) CPU cache Cowboy Violin Humerus Whip Dialysis RISC Treasure Island Lindy Basic Electrical wiring Whose Line Is It Anyway? Expanded Universe (Star Wars) Pontiac's Rebellion My Little Pony Breaststroke Heart rate Tallit Margin of error Mount Pinatubo Hip dysplasia Music of Canada The Beatles bootlegs Breech birth Woodworking Roots of hip hop music Good Morning, Vietnam Russian joke Hudson's Bay Company Geodesy Chest Loudspeaker Hip hop rivalries Surveillance 